      "review_summary": "The PR wraps OpenRouter music SSE JSON parsing in a try/catch, adds mocked and localhost HTTP regression tests, and adds a standalone loopback proof script.\n\nPR surface: Source +6, Tests +154. Total +160 across 3 files.\n\nReproducibility: yes. source-reproducible: current main calls JSON.parse(data) for each non-empty non-[DONE] OpenRouter music SSE data line, so malformed JSON throws before later valid frames can be processed. I did not run a live OpenRouter malformed-frame reproduction in this read-only review.",
      "review_followup": "- [P1] The remaining action combines contributor-supplied real provider proof, a small lint repair, and possible maintainer acceptance of loopback-only evidence, so this should stay in human PR review rather than an automated repair lane.",
